#. type: Plain text
#: tools/translation-ai-prompts/prompt.txt:4
msgid ""
"We're translating board game rule book from English to [...].  The text is "
"in LaTeX format, and the messages are in GNU gettext po format.  Rules:"
msgstr ""
"We're translating board game rule book from English to Hungarian. The text "
"is in LaTeX format, and the messages are in GNU gettext po format. Rules:"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
#: tools/translation-ai-prompts/prompt.txt:17
msgid "PO Format Rules. Both msgid and msgstr should:"
msgstr "PO formátumszabályok. A msgid és a msgstr egyaránt:"

#. type: Bullet: '   - '
#: tools/translation-ai-prompts/prompt.txt:17
msgid "Start with an empty quoted string: `\"\"`"
msgstr "Kezdődjön egy üres idézőjeles karakterlánccal: `\"\"`"

#. type: Bullet: '   - '
#: tools/translation-ai-prompts/prompt.txt:17
msgid "Have each line on a new line"
msgstr "Minden sor külön új sorba kerüljön"

#. type: Bullet: '   - '
#: tools/translation-ai-prompts/prompt.txt:17
msgid "Have each line surrounded by quotes"
msgstr "Minden sor idézőjelek közé kerüljön"

#. type: Plain text
#: tools/translation-ai-prompts/prompt.txt:17
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"   - End each quoted line with \\n\n"
"   Example:\n"
"   msgid \"\"\n"
"   \"First line\\n\"\n"
"   \"Second line\\n\"\n"
"   msgstr \"\"\n"
"   \"[...]\\n\"\n"
"   \"[...]\\n\"\n"
msgstr ""
"   - End each quoted line with \\n\n"
"   Example:\n"
"   msgid \"\"\n"
"   \"First line\\n\"\n"
"   \"Second line\\n\"\n"
"   msgstr \"\"\n"
"   \"Első sor\\n\"\n"
"   \"Második sor\\n\"\n"

#. type: Bullet: '2. '
#: tools/translation-ai-prompts/prompt.txt:38
msgid "LaTeX Commands"
msgstr "LaTeX parancsok"

#. type: Bullet: '   - '
#: tools/translation-ai-prompts/prompt.txt:38
msgid "Preserve all whitespace at the start of lines"
msgstr "Őrizd meg a sorok elején lévő összes szóközt"

#. type: Bullet: '   - '
#: tools/translation-ai-prompts/prompt.txt:38
msgid "Keep all LaTeX commands exactly as they appear"
msgstr "Minden LaTeX parancs pontosan úgy maradjon, ahogy eredetileg szerepel"

#. type: Bullet: '   - '
#: tools/translation-ai-prompts/prompt.txt:38
msgid ""
"`\\pagetarget{...}{...}`: The first argument is not translated. For example, "
"`\\pagetarget{Heroes}{Heroes}` translates to `\\pagetarget{Heroes}{[...]}`."
msgstr ""
"`\\pagetarget{...}{...}`: The first argument is not translated. For example, "
"`\\pagetarget{Heroes}{Heroes}` translates to `\\pagetarget{Heroes}{Hősök}`."

#. type: Bullet: '   - '
#: tools/translation-ai-prompts/prompt.txt:38
msgid ""
"`\\pagelink{...}{...}`: The first argument is not translated. For example, "
"`\\pagelink{Combatexperience}{Combat}` translates to "
"`\\pagelink{Combatexperience}{[...]}`."
msgstr ""
"`\\pagelink{...}{...}`: The first argument is not translated. For example, "
"`\\pagelink{Combatexperience}{Combat}` translates to "
"`\\pagelink{Combatexperience}{Harc}`."

#. type: Bullet: '   - '
#: tools/translation-ai-prompts/prompt.txt:38
msgid ""
"`\\index{...}`: The content within the `\\index{...}` command is translated."
msgstr "`\\index{...}`: A `\\index{...}` parancson belüli tartalom lefordítandó."

#. type: Bullet: '   - '
#: tools/translation-ai-prompts/prompt.txt:38
msgid "Do not translate LaTeX command names"
msgstr "Ne fordítsd le a LaTeX parancsneveket"

#. type: Bullet: '   - '
#: tools/translation-ai-prompts/prompt.txt:38
msgid "Do not add or remove line breaks (\\n)"
msgstr "Ne adj hozzá és ne távolíts el sortöréseket (\\n)"

#. type: Bullet: '   - '
#: tools/translation-ai-prompts/prompt.txt:38
msgid "Maintain all whitespace around LaTeX commands"
msgstr "Őrizd meg a LaTeX parancsok körüli összes szóközt"

#. type: Bullet: '   - '
#: tools/translation-ai-prompts/prompt.txt:38
msgid "Maintain line breaks exactly as they appear in the source text"
msgstr "Őrizd meg a sortöréseket pontosan úgy, ahogy a forrásszövegben szerepelnek"

#. type: Bullet: '   - '
#: tools/translation-ai-prompts/prompt.txt:38
msgid "Special commands to keep unchanged:"
msgstr "Változatlanul hagyandó speciális parancsok:"

#. type: Bullet: '     - '
#: tools/translation-ai-prompts/prompt.txt:38
msgid "SVG icons (\\svg{damage-yellow})"
msgstr "SVG ikonok (\\svg{damage-yellow})"

#. type: Bullet: '     - '
#: tools/translation-ai-prompts/prompt.txt:38
msgid "Spacing commands (\\bigskip, \\hsize, etc.)"
msgstr "Térközparancsok (\\bigskip, \\hsize stb.)"

#. type: Bullet: '   - '
#: tools/translation-ai-prompts/prompt.txt:38
msgid "For tables (like \\hommtable, \\tabularx):"
msgstr "Táblázatoknál (például \\hommtable, \\tabularx):"

#. type: Bullet: '     - '
#: tools/translation-ai-prompts/prompt.txt:38
msgid "Keep all sizing parameters unchanged (e.g., {38}, {0.3\\hsize})"
msgstr "Minden méretezési paraméter maradjon változatlan (pl. {38}, {0.3\\hsize})"

#. type: Bullet: '     - '
#: tools/translation-ai-prompts/prompt.txt:38
msgid "Preserve all cell styling commands (\\darkcell, \\lightcell)"
msgstr "Őrizd meg az összes cellastílus-parancsot (\\darkcell, \\lightcell)"

#. type: Plain text
#: tools/translation-ai-prompts/prompt.txt:38
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"     - Maintain table column specifications\n"
"   Example:\n"
"   msgid \"\\\\darkcell[1.5]{\\\\color{white}Game Difficulty}\"\n"
"   msgstr \"\\\\darkcell[1.5]{\\\\color{white}[...]}\"\n"
msgstr ""
"     - Maintain table column specifications\n"
"   Example:\n"
"   msgid \"\\\\darkcell[1.5]{\\\\color{white}Game Difficulty}\"\n"
"   msgstr \"\\\\darkcell[1.5]{\\\\color{white}Játék nehézség}\"\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: tools/translation-ai-prompts/prompt.txt:42
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"3. Capitalization\n"
"Maintain the capitalization of the words as in the original text.\n"
"If in English there is \"Hero\", the translation should also be capitalized.\n"
msgstr ""
"3. Nagybetűhasználat\n"
"Őrizd meg a szavak nagybetűzését az eredeti szövegnek megfelelően.\n"
"Ha angolul \"Hero\" szerepel, akkor a fordításban is nagybetűvel szerepeljen (\"Hős\", ne \"hős\").\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: tools/translation-ai-prompts/prompt.txt:48
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"4. Example\n"
"Given the following `msgid`:\n"
"\"  \\\\pagetarget{Heroes}{Players} always control a Main Hero and may additionally also recruit a Secondary Hero.\\n\"\n"
"The output should be:\n"
"\"  \\\\pagetarget{Heroes}{[...]} [...]\\n\"\n"
msgstr ""
"4. Példa\n"
"A következő `msgid` esetén:\n"
"\"  \\\\pagetarget{Heroes}{Players} always control a Main Hero and may additionally also recruit a Secondary Hero.\\n\"\n"
"A kimenetnek ennek kell lennie:\n"
"\"  \\\\pagetarget{Heroes}{Játékosok} mindig egy Főhőst irányítanak, és emellett egy Mellékhőst is toborozhatnak.\\n\"\n"

#. type: Bullet: '5. '
#: tools/translation-ai-prompts/prompt.txt:54
msgid "Output"
msgstr "Kimenet"

#. type: Bullet: '  - '
#: tools/translation-ai-prompts/prompt.txt:54
msgid "Output a copyable code block"
msgstr "A kimenet legyen másolható kódblokk"

#. type: Bullet: '  - '
#: tools/translation-ai-prompts/prompt.txt:54
msgid ""
"Output just the translated `msgstr` given the `msgid`, maintaining the "
"original formatting and quotes."
msgstr "Csak a lefordított `msgstr` legyen a kimenet a megadott `msgid` alapján, az eredeti formázás és idézőjelek megtartásával."

#. type: Bullet: '  - '
#: tools/translation-ai-prompts/prompt.txt:54
msgid "If the code block starts with a line `msgstr \"\"`, omit this line"
msgstr "Ha a kódblokk `msgstr \"\"` sorral kezdődik, hagyd ki ezt a sort"

#. type: Bullet: '  - '
#: tools/translation-ai-prompts/prompt.txt:54
msgid "The block should include the final newline"
msgstr "A blokk tartalmazza a záró újsor karaktert is"

